<h1>Ikat Craft of Telangana</h1>
<p>
Tradition Woven Into Every Thread.
Ikat is a traditional handloom weaving technique known for its intricate dyeing and weaving process.
Lingala Ghanpur in Telangana is emerging as an important Ikat weaving cluster preserving cultural heritage through handmade textiles.
</p>
</header>
