<h2>Artisans of Lingala Ghanpur</h2>
<p style="text-align:center; max-width:900px; margin:auto; font-size:18px;">
The Ikat weaving community includes skilled artisans who contribute to different stages of weaving.
Women actively participate in yarn preparation, dyeing, and weaving processes.
Their contribution helps preserve the tradition for future generations.
</p>
</div>
