<!-- PROCESS -->
<section id="process">
<div class="container">
<h2>Making Process of Ikat</h2>

<div class="process-steps">

<div class="step">
<h3>1. Yarn Boiling</h3>
<p>Threads are cleaned and prepared for dyeing.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>2. Winding</h3>
<p>Yarn is wound carefully onto bobbins.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>3. Design Marking</h3>
<p>Patterns are marked on yarns before dyeing.</p>
</div>
<div class="step">
<h3>4. Tying</h3>
<p>Selected sections are tied to resist dye.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>5. Dyeing</h3>
<p>Yarns are dyed in vibrant colours.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>6. Drying</h3>
<p>Dyed yarns are sun-dried and inspected.</p>
</div>

<div class="step">
<h3>7. Weaving</h3>
<p>Fabric is woven carefully on pit looms.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
